Package: testCahoy
Title: Bootstrap Test for Equality of Variances
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Kornelia", "Kozaczewska", email = "lacinakornelia@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Implementation of the bootstrap test for equality of variances
    proposed by Cahoy (2010) <doi:10.1016/j.csda.2010.04.012>, a
    resampling-based alternative to Bartlett's and Levene's tests, robust
    under non-normality and small samples.
